sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>8085/TCP gRPC<br/>mTLS (configurable)
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>TLS (configurable)
    participant GenSvc as Generation Service<br/>(TGIS 8033 / Caikit 8085)<br/>gRPC mTLS (configurable)
    participant vLLM as OpenAI Service (vLLM)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>TLS (configurable)

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 1: Unary Generation with Detection (v2 API)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/generation-detection<br/>mTLS (optional)
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk input text<br/>mm-model-id header
    Chunker-->>Orch: Text chunks
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Bearer token — input detection
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    Orch->>GenSvc: Generate(prompt)<br/>mm-model-id header
    GenSvc-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk generated text<br/>mm-model-id header
    Chunker-->>Orch: Output chunks
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Bearer token — output detection
    Detector-->>Orch: Output detection results
    Orch-->>Client: Combined generation + detection response

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completions (OpenAI-compatible)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>SSE stream, mTLS (optional)
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/chat<br/>Bearer token — input detection on last message
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection result

    Orch->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Bearer token — SSE streaming
    loop Streaming tokens via broadcast channels
        vLLM-->>Orch: SSE chunk (token)
        Orch->>Chunker: BidiStreaming chunk tokens<br/>mm-model-id header
        Chunker-->>Orch: Assembled text chunk
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Bearer token — output detection on chunk
        Detector-->>Orch: Chunk detection result
        Note over Orch: DetectionBatcher orders results<br/>(CompletionBatcher for multi-choice)
        Orch-->>Client: SSE event (token + detection)
    end
    Orch-->>Client: SSE [DONE]

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 3: Standalone Content Detection
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>mTLS (optional)
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk input text<br/>mm-model-id header
    Chunker-->>Orch: Text chunks
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Bearer token
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: Detection response
